videos.description: 1H (17:24) PUR P.J. Thompson made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Vince Edwards.
videos.headline: Slick move leads to open 3 for Purdue

videos.description: Louisville moving the ball around, they get it to Ray Spalding, who finishes with the dunk.
videos.headline: Great passing leads to Louisville dunk

videos.description: Donovan Mitchell gets the ball to Ray Spalding, who gets another dunk for Louisville.
videos.headline: Pick-and-roll play gets Ray Spalding another big dunk

videos.description: Carson Edwards tries to score for Purdue, but Ray Spalding gets the block.  Louisville heading the other way, Deng Adel eventually gets it and hits a 3-pointer to extend the Cardinals' lead.
videos.headline: Louisville uses big block to spark offense
Louisville ends first half with a buzzer beater
